---
layout: base.njk
title: Fight for Manhood
---

<section class="hero">
  <div style="max-width:980px; margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:center;">
      <div style="display:inline-block; padding:6px 12px; border:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,.35); border-radius:999px; font-size:13px; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,.85); background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);">
        Knoxville • Wednesdays • 6:00 PM • No cost
      </div>
      <div style="display:inline-block; padding:6px 12px; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14); border-radius:999px; font-size:13px; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,.80); background:rgba(0,0,0,.18);">
        {% cohortCountdown %} • {% cohortStartLabel %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-top:22px;">Surrender to God.</h2>
    <h2 style="color:var(--gold); margin-top:-8px;">Fight like a man.</h2>

    <p class="muted" style="margin-top:22px; font-size:24px; max-width:860px;">
      A 10-week Christian leadership program that forges real men.
    </p>

    <div style="margin:22px auto 0; max-width:860px; border:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,.22); background:rgba(212,175,55,.06); border-radius:14px; padding:14px 16px;">
      <div style="font-weight:900; letter-spacing:.2px;">
        Next Cohort: <span style="color:var(--gold);">{% cohortCountdown %}</span> • <span style="color:var(--gold);">{% cohortStartLabel %}</span> • Goal: <span style="color:var(--gold);">20 men</span>
      </div>
      <div class="muted" style="margin-top:6px; font-size:14px;">
        We’re building the next cohort now. If you’re in, lock it in.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:26px;">
      <a class="button" href="/apply/">Register Now</a>
      <a class="button" style="background:transparent; color:var(--gold); border:1px solid var(--gold);" href="/program/">See the Program</a>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:28px; display:flex; gap:14px; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:center; color:rgba(255,255,255,.75); font-size:14px;">
      <div style="border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); padding:10px 14px; border-radius:10px; background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);">
        <strong style="color:#fff;">10 weeks</strong> • 2 hours/night
      </div>
      <div style="border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); padding:10px 14px; border-radius:10px; background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);">
        <strong style="color:#fff;">High challenge</strong> • High support
      </div>
      <div style="border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); padding:10px 14px; border-radius:10px; background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);">
        <strong style="color:#fff;">Confidential</strong> • Men only
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h3>The Problem</h3>
  <p style="font-size:22px; max-width:920px;">
    Most men aren’t weak. They’re <strong>unfocused</strong>.
  </p>
  <p class="muted" style="max-width:920px;">
    We fight the wrong battles. We withdraw when we should lead. We perform instead of surrender.
    Strength without surrender becomes control. Surrender without strength becomes passivity.
  </p>

  <div style="margin-top:22px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px;">
    <div style="border:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,.20); background:rgba(255,255,255,.02); border-radius:14px; padding:18px;">
      <div style="color:var(--gold); font-weight:900; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:13px;">Drift</div>
      <div class="muted" style="margin-top:6px;">No aim. No standard. No momentum.</div>
    </div>
    <div style="border:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,.20); background:rgba(255,255,255,.02); border-radius:14px; padding:18px;">
      <div style="color:var(--gold); font-weight:900; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:13px;">Isolation</div>
      <div class="muted" style="margin-top:6px;">Men disappear instead of showing up.</div>
    </div>
    <div style="border:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,.20); background:rgba(255,255,255,.02); border-radius:14px; padding:18px;">
      <div style="color:var(--gold); font-weight:900; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:13px;">Shame</div>
      <div class="muted" style="margin-top:6px;">Hidden battles kill leadership.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top:26px; border-top:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,.22);"></div>
  <style>
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .section div[style*="grid-template-columns:repeat(3"] { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    }
  </style>
</section>

<section class="section" style="text-align:center;">
  <h3>Register Now</h3>
  <p class="muted" style="max-width:820px; margin:0 auto;">
    Next cohort <strong style="color:var(--gold);">{% cohortCountdown %}</strong> — <strong style="color:var(--gold);">{% cohortStartLabel %}</strong>.
    Register now and we’ll send you the details.
  </p>
  <div style="margin-top:26px;">
    <a class="button" href="/apply/">Register for the Next Cohort</a>
  </div>
</section>
